64
00:05:11,779 --> 00:05:18,219
tachycardia, stomach discomfort, nausea and headache.

65
00:05:18,219 --> 00:05:23,819
Toxic effects like seizures can be seen after the rapid consumption of around 1200mg of

66
00:05:23,819 --> 00:05:24,819
caffeine.

67
00:05:24,819 --> 00:05:29,860
That's the equivalent of around 12 cups of coffee.

68
00:05:29,860 --> 00:05:32,939
Of course these limits vary from person to person.

69
00:05:32,939 --> 00:05:36,740
